Candidate Privacy Statement
Manychat, Inc., together with all its affiliates and subsidiaries (hereinafter referred to as “
we
”, “
us
”, and the “
Company
”) is committed to protecting your personal data and respecting your privacy. The Company is committed to collecting and further processing your personal data pursuant to the applicable data protection regulations in the countries where the Company operates.
